{"tid":359231,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[華人一哥] 走投無路 前騎師鄭雨滇被追744萬貸款","createTime":"2017-08-14T10:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T11:30:42.000Z","uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc9b106e76e35e5634ed1f70fd3d0246a00fdaa","tid":359231,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170814/mobile/bkn-20170814112246782-0814_00822_001.html#popupGallery\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170814%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170814112246782-0814_00822_001.html%23popupGallery&h=762f8fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年4月被香港賽馬會釘牌的前騎師鄭雨滇，被一間放債人公司入稟高等法院追討兩筆貸款，合共約744萬港元欠款和利息。原告迅興信貸有限公司，兩名被告依次是鄭雨滇和勞狄欣。 <br />\n<br />\n入稟狀指稱，原告於2015年8月31日與兩名被告簽訂貸款協議，並於同日借出605萬港元給兩名被告，該筆貸款每年利息是26厘。原告於2016年3月29日與兩名被告簽訂另一份貸款協議，就分期還款作出安排，兩名被告自2016年開始沒有按協議分期還款，截至本月8日，兩名被告欠原告本金連利息共約737.84萬港元。原告要求高院下令兩名被告還款。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，原告於2015年8月31日與鄭簽訂了另一份個人貸款協議，並借出10萬港元給他，該筆個人貸款每年利息是48厘，截至本月8日，鄭欠原告本金和利息6.18萬港元。原告要求高院下令鄭還款。 <br />\n<br />\n做騎師唔係搵好多架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7fe46be9aa307fa29e058b69552d25ac1ef67ad","tid":359231,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:44:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170814/mobile/bkn-20170814112246782-0814_00822_001.html#popupGallery\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170814%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170814112246782-0814_00822_001.html%23popupGallery&d=eILJjGo7kX%2BklWE%2BFO9zci7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=0f62ea59\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170814/mobile/bkn-20170814112246782-0814_00822_001.html#popupGallery</a>"},{"pid":"0c639ced9022ad768ed24e5f55532c9f6fb5fe5c","tid":359231,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:45:43.000Z","msg":"上到庭重複返&quot;喂喂喂喂!....